Carnage/ Teltoli

* Carnage watched Cyber Claw kick in her sleep but kept backing up and 
making Teltoli back up with her, if the clone was suddenly going to attack 
then she wanter herself to be the one to get hit first and not Teltoli.
Suddenly she was forced to stop by a jolt from behind, they'd backed up into 
a tree trunk and couldn't go back any further.
Teltoli snarled as one shoulder hit the tree and the other got bumped by 
Carnage...*

Teltoli:"HAY!"

* Carnage looked back at Teltoli and snarled at her, the Fuzor just yelled 
loud enough to wake the dead!
Carnage then looked ahead of her and at the clone, she took a step 
forward...waiting to see what happened next!*
